##  EXTRA NOTES




-  helm repo add <repo-name> <repo url > 
-  helm repo add prometheus-community https //prometheus-community.github.io/helm-charts  // we give alias to repo 
-  The added repo is stored in Helm’s config directory (~/.config/helm/repositories.yaml).
-  - caFile: ""
  certFile: ""
  insecure_skip_tls_verify: false
  keyFile: ""
  name: bitnami
  pass_credentials_all: false
  password: ""
  url: https://charts.bitnami.com/bitnami
  username: ""
-  in ~/.cache/helm/repository
-  bitnami-charts.txt  bitnami-index.yaml 

-  helm repo remove <reponame>

-  helm search repo

- helm index <chart-name>

-  helm lint <release-name> // checks its syntax   , and  it is before it is installing or making its releases

- helm history <release-name> flags  // to check revisions of helm

diff plugin  in 2 releases we updated the replicas ,helm plugin - install, list, or uninstall Helm plugins 
-  helm diff revision <release-name> 1 2

- helm install <release-name> —debug —dry-run <chart-name >
